    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to save your family, you must venture from home in order to find and return a dragon’s egg. Catsploration is a high fantasy adventure with narrative and 3D platforming elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710260/extras/71003438062d0106a9ac613097c6da5e.poster.avif?t=1767037073\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710260/extras/71003438062d0106a9ac613097c6da5e.webm?t=1767037073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710260/extras/71003438062d0106a9ac613097c6da5e.mp4?t=1767037073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your search for Magneteia's lost egg will take you all across Driftstone. You must explore lost caves and navigate through dangerous hazards in order to gather what you need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710260/extras/fba068b0d33fd9b052bfc48272b21ffc.webp?t=1767037073\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710260/extras/fba068b0d33fd9b052bfc48272b21ffc.poster.webp?t=1767037073\" class=\"bb_img\" width=620 height=180 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A narrative-driven adventure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy hand-crafted environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jumping puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collectibles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catsploration takes place in a world consistent with Pathfinder 2e. We tell a short level 0 adventure, without combat.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although Catsploration is a solo indie game, made by me, Paul, this game also includes content made by hundreds of individuals. Please take the time to see the in game credits menu to learn more.</p>",
